feedback.title: Great Service
feedback.content: I had an excellent experience with the customer service team. They were very helpful and resolved my issue quickly.

feedback.title: Average Experience
feedback.content: The service was okay, but there is room for improvement. The wait time was longer than expected.

feedback.title: Excellent Customer Service
feedback.content: I had a fantastic experience with the customer service team. They were very responsive and helpful.

feedback.title: Poor Service
feedback.content: I am disappointed with the service I received. My issue was not resolved and I had to wait a long time for assistance.
